  10. Ai3 Khau3 Bo5 Bak8-sai2. 
  Chin-chiaN3 si7 ai3 khau3 bo5 bak8-sai2, sim na2-chun2 beh piak-lih8 e5 kan-khou2, hin7 be7-tit chek-si5 chhah-sit8 poe kau3 ai3-jin5 e5 sin-piN. Peng5-si5 m7-bat khi3 kau3 tang-pou7, chu7 tah8-chhut piN7-iN7 e5 kha kin2 chau2 kau3 chhia-cham7, khi3 be2 chit8 tiuN khoai3-chhia-phio3, kau3 Tai5-pak tou i2-keng koe3-tau3 au7 lah. Tui3 hia koh choan2 chhia kau3 Sou-ou3. Ti7 lou7-tiong u7 Ku-soaN e5 keng2-ti3, ian5-lou7 chin sui2, sek8-iong5 chio3 ti7 hai2-bin7, hong5-hun kui-phang5 e5 hi5-chun5 e5 bi2-keng2, tui3 ti7 i long2 bo5 i3-gi7 lah. Sim chat8 thong2-thong2, siong5-siong5 thau lau5 bak8-sai2. Kau3 Sou-ou3 i2-keng am3 lah, Sou-Hoa kong-lou7 e5 khi3-chhia i2-keng koe3 si5-kan, tioh8 tan2-hau7 bin5-a2 cha2-khi2 chiah u7 koh hoat-chhia. TaN beh chaiN2-iuN7, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2-lang5 m7-bat poaN3 e5 lang5, chin chhiN-sou, m7-bat chhut-goa7 chiah hng7. Na7 siuN7 beh khi3 hioh lu2-sia7, iu7 siuN7 tioh8 ti7 nng7-goeh8 goa7 jit8 cheng5 ti7 Tai5-tiong Ka-pin lu2-sia7 e5 su7. Ji7-ho7-pang5 e5 khoan2-sit, na2-chun2 ti7 bak8-cheng5 hian7-hian7, siuN7 liau2 put-kak sim koh phok8-phok8-chheng2 chin kiaN. Sou2-i2 m-kaN2 siuN7 beh khi3 hioh lu2-sia7, kiaN5 lai5 kiaN5 khi3 chin ia3-sian7, au7-lai5 khi3 chhia-cham7 che7. Che7 kau3 chin am3, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 kiaN, che ia7 m7-si7 pan7-hoat. Au7-lai5 u7 chit8 e5 keng2-chhat lai5, chiah pai3-thok i chhoa7 i khi3 pai3-tng5 keh-mi5. 
  Keh cha2-khi2 bo5 khoa3 chiah8-png7, chiu7 khi3 chhia-cham7, bok8-su-niu5 lau5 i chiah8-png7, i hui-siong5 e5 kheh-khi3, au7-lai5 ti7 chhia-thau5 be2 mi7-pau chi2-ki, chu7 chhut-mng5 kau3 cha2-khi2 chiah chiah8. Au7-lai5 che7 chhia. Sou-Hoa kong-lou7 e5 chhia, sui-jian5 si7 khi3-chhia (chu7-tong7-chhia) iau2-ku2 na2 hoe2-chhia le3, khioh kui pang chiah hoat, u7-si5 chit8 pang 7, 8 tai5 chhia, chit8 tai5 che7 iok 50 lang5. In-ui7 lou7 eh8, chit8 bin7 soaN, chit8 bin7 hai2, hai2 to7 si7 Thai3-peng5-iuN5, hit-e5 keng2-ti3 hui-siong5 sui2. Tek8-piat8 lou7-tiong u7 keng-koe3 Chheng-chui2 toan7-gai5, u7-si5 hai2-bin7 ta3-bu7 u7 kheng7, chhia oan2-jian5 chau2 ti7 hun5-bu7 e5 kheng7-teng2, chin-chiaN3 u7 “U2-hoa3 teng-sian” e5 kam2-khai3. Na2-chun2 hoat-sit8 poe chiuN7 thiN e5 chhu3-bi7. Sui-jian5 si7 chiah sui2 e5 keng2-ti3, Lan5-hiong long2 bo5 kam2-kak. Chin-chiaN3 si7 sim chat8-chat8, chi2-u7 Chheng-choaN5 e5 bin7-iaN2, kap Ji7-ho7-pang5 e5 cheng5-heng5. Loan5-ai3, loan7-ai3 tau3-ti2 si7 tiN, a2-si7 khou2 ah? Siong5-siong5 theh8 chhiu2-kin-a2 khi2 lai5 thau chhit bak8-sai2. 
  PeN7-iN7 si5-chit khi3, it-sim beh chhoe7 cheng5-jin5, kau3 hit mng2-pou chiah kau3 Hoa-lian5. Hit e7-tau3 bo5 chiah8, ia7 m7-chai iau. Loh8-chhia chek-si5 kio3 saN-lian2-chhia lai5 che7, chhiaN2 i ka7 i thoa khi3 Tiong-cheng3-lou7 35 ho7. Kau3-ui7 loh8-chhia, taN-thau5 chit8 e7 khoaN3, m7-si7 phoe5-e5 tiam3, si7 se2-saN-a2 tiam3. Tioh8 chit8 kiaN ka7 thoa-chhia--e5 kong2, Li2 kiam2 thoa tioh8 ui7? I kong2 bo5 chho3. Chiu7 loh8 khi3 mng7 hit keng se2-saN-a2 tiam3 e5 lau2-pan2 kong2, “Lin2 chia kiam2 m7-si7 Tiong-cheng3-lou7 35 ho7?” “Si7.” “Kiam2 m7-si7 Hoa-bi2 phoe5-e5 tiam3?” “M7-si7.” “Bo5, lin2 chia kiam2 u7 Hoa-bi2 phoe5-e5 tiam3?” “Bo5.” Lan5-hiong soa3 gang7-gang7, na2-chun2 hou7 tian7 tian7--tioh8 chit8-iuN7, tiam7-tiam7 khia7 tit ho2-ku2, chiah koh mng7 kong2, “Lin2 chia u7 chit8 e5 kio3-choe3 Tan5 Chin3-seng5 a2-bo5?” Hit-e5 lang5 in3 kong2, “Bo5.” “Ia7 in kiaN2 kio3-choe3 Tan5 Chheng-choaN5 lin2 bat thiaN-kiN3--bo5?” “M7-bat.” Kau3-chia lai5 Lan5-hiong kha long2 nng2 chit8 koeh8 lah. KhoaN3 lai5 kau3 chiah hng7, m7-bat poaN3-e5 lang5, te7-hng, lang5-bin7 long2 chhiN-sou, chai oan5-choan5 hou7 Chheng-choaN5 phian3-khi3 lah. Chin-chiaN3 si7 ai3 si2 be7 tng7-khui3. KhoaN3 chit8 e5 lang5 ho2 ho2 m7 choe3, si7 peN7-iN7 sou2 tui3-tiong7 e5 hou7-su7 pan-tiuN2, si7 Ki-tok-kau3 ka-teng5 e5 lu2-chu2. Lai5 thiaN chit e5 be7 ioh8-a2 chau2 kang-ou5 e5 lang5 e5 chhui3. Bo5 tham3-thiaN, bo5 mng7 pe7-bo2, bo5 bo2 ma7 iau2-u7 pe7. Bo5 ki5-to2, kan-taN thiaN tiN-bit8 e5 oe7, na2-chun2 hou-sin5 chi2-u7 khoaN3 tioh8 thng5, m7-chai kong2 kiaN5-jip8 hou-sin5-tng e5 lai7-bin7, e7 chau2 be7 tit chhut--lai5. 
  Mng7 long2 bo5, chin kian3-siau3, ia7 khi3, ia7 kiaN, ia7 sit-bang7, ban7-kam2 kau-chip8. Chin-chiaN3 si7 ai3 khau3 bo5 bak8-sai2. Bak8-sai2 long2 kian loh8-khi3, bak8-khou ang5-ang5, chu7 an2-ni phaiN2-se3, phaiN2-se3, bin7 kin2 oat8 piN-a2 kiaN5 li7-khui hit-keng se2-saN-a2 tiam3. Hit-si5 jit8 iau2 kng-kng, m7 kam-goan7, na2 siau2 cha-bou2 leh, eng7 kiaN5--e5, chhiu2 koaN7 chit8-sut-a2 tan2-lou7, beh hou7 bi7-lai5 e5 ta-koaN, koaN7 teh tong7-tong7-hiN3, chau2-pian3 Hoa-lian5-chhi7 beh jin7-chin ka7 i chhoe7 khoaN3 u7 Hoa-bi2 phoe5-e5 tiam3 a2-bo5, khah-chhoe7 tou chhoe7 bo5. Chhoe7 kau3 am3, nng7-ki kha nge7 khok-khok, kha-te2 long2 phong3-pha7. U7 kui2-na7 pai2 kiaN5 tui3 pai3-tng5 cheng5 koe3, na7-si7 kau3 chia ia7 bo5 hit ho7 iong2-khi3 thang jip8-khi3 mng7 bok8-su. Kau3 chia sin-the2 sim-sin5 long2 chin ia3-sian7 lah. Chu7 an2-ni thoa tim5-tang7 e5 kha, ban7-ban7 ng3 pak-peng5 e5 toa7-lou7 bong2 kiaN5. Si5 ia7 bo5 cha2 lah, tui3 hia koh khi3 chiu7-si7 Bi2-lun5. Kau3 Bi2-lun5 kio5-teng2 che7 tiam3 hia hau2 chit8 khun3. Hut-jian5 siuN7 khi2 cha2-jit8 kam-tiN e5 bi2-keng2, Chheng-choaN5 sou2 bat chhiuN3 hou7 i thiaN e5 liu5-heng5 koa. 
