  11. Ki5-sit8 Tau3-ti2 Si7 ChaiN2-iuN7? 
  Kha tu2 haN7 koe3 kio5-niu5 beh thiau3 loh8-khi3, au7-bin7 tu2 gu7 chit8 e5 keng2-chhat khia5 chu7-choan2-chhia sun5-lo5 lai5 kau3 hia, goan5-in si7 i tui3 hng7-hng7 i2-keng thiaN-kiN3 chit kak-si3 u7 cha-bou2 lang5 teh khau3 e5 siaN, ji5-chhiaN2 hit-e5 siaN si7 chin chhiN-chham2, sou2-i2 i chiah e7 sun5 tui3 chit peng5 lai5. Thiau3 loh8 chhia beh ka7 i giu2 leh i2-keng siuN7 ban7, khiu2 bo5 tiau5, au7-bin7 e5 saN-a2-ki giu2-phoa3 lih8 chin hng7, kiat-kiok8 iu5-goan5 si7 poah8 loh8 khi3. Goan5-lai5 chit tiau5 khe li7 hai2 i2-keng chin kin7, koh khi3 chiu7-si7 hai2-kiN5, chui2 se3 ban7, na7-si7 siong-tong chhim, keng2-chhat chu7 an2-ni toe3 i thiau3 loh8-khi3, chit8 si5 Lan5-hiong u7 tim5 loh8-khi3, au7-lai5 koh phu5 khi2-lai5, keng2-chhat tui3 thau5-chang ka7 i giu2 leh, siu5 5, 6 pou7 chiu7 peh chiuN7 hoaN7, ka7 i giu2 chiuN7 hoaN7 e5 si5 seng-khu tam5 lok-lok, ia7 chiah8 kui2-na7 chhui3 chui2; ka-chai3 hit si5 i2-keng chin am3, na7 bo5, lang5 un2-tang3 e7 toe3 kui-tin7. I ia7 tam5, keng2-chhat ia7 tam5, nng7 e5 seng-khu long2 tam5 lok-lok, na2 chun2 loh8-thng-ke chit8-iuN7. Keng2-chhat chu7 an2-ni toa3 i khi3 phai3-chhut-sou2. 
  Keng2-chhat ho2-i3 kio3 i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 chhut-lai5 chiap Lan5-hiong jip8-khi3 oaN7 ta e5 saN-khou3. Keng2-chhat ia7 khi3 oaN7 saN, oaN7 liau2 chiah mng7 i si7 ui7 sim2-mih8 in-toaN beh thiau3 chui2 chu7-sat; Lan5-hiong chiu7 chiong5-thau5 kau3-boe2 tai7-liok8 kong2 hou7 i thiaN. Hit si5 tu2 am3-si5 e5 11 tiam2 goa7, hit-e5 keng2-chhat chu7 an2-ni toa3 Lan5-hiong kap khau2-keng choe3-hoe2 khi3 keng2-chhat-kiok8. In-ui7 phai3-chhut-sou2 bo5 tu2-ho2 e5 sou2-chai7 thang po2-hou7, kau3 keng2-chhat-kiok8 i2-keng chiaN5 poaN3-mi5 lah, sou2-i2 liam-piN siat-hoat hou7 i tiam3 ti7 hu7-lu2 e5 hiu-khe2-sek, hou7 i ti7 hia keh chit8 mi5, ke3-jit8 koh-chai3 siong5-se3 mng7 khau2-keng, kiok8-tiuN2 iok-sok beh the3 i tiau-cha. Kiok8-tiuN2 hian2-beng5 chap8-hun e5 tong5-cheng5; jit8 beh am3 keng2-chhat theh8 Lan5-hiong ka-ki7 thng3 khi2-lai5 phak8 e5 saN-khou3 lai5 hou7 i koh oaN7 to3-tng2, koh keh-jit8 keng2-chhat-kiok8-tiuN2 chiu7 phai3 hit-e5 kiu3 i e5 keng2-chhat ka7 i po2-hou7, sang3 i to3-khi3 kau3 SoaN-pa3 kau in lau7-pe7. 
  Choe7-ok e5 kang-chiN5 chiu7-si7 si2. Li2 khoaN3, ui7-tioh8 tham-loan5 chit8-si5 jiok8-the2 cheng5-iok8 e5 khoai3-lok8, lai5 ti3-kau3 cheng-chho siu7 thun2-tah8, jian5-au7 hou7 lang5 hiat-kak8, chit ho7 su7 m7-si7 hian7-si5 chiah u7. Li2 khoaN3 kou2-cha2 Ku7-iok si5-tai7 Tai7-pit8 e5 kiaN2 Am3-lun5 ke2-piN7, ai3 Ap-sa-liong5 e5 sio2-moai7 Tha-ma2 khi3 khoaN3--i, in-ui7 i tham-loan5 Tha-ma2 e5 sui2, kio3 Tha-ma2 theh8 mih8 khi3 piN7-chhng5 hou7 i chiah8, kau3 keng3-jian5 ka7 i kiong5-u3, phah la5-sam5--i, au7-lai5 m7-tih8--i, nge7-nge7 ka7 i koaN2 chhut-khi3 (Ⅱ Sat-bo2-jiN2 13: 1—19). Am3-lun5 kap Tha-ma2 si7 siang7 pe7 bo5 siang7 bo2 e5 hiaN-moai7, siong7-chhiaN2 kaN2 an2-ni choe3, ho5-hong3 chit tiap8 e5 lang5, (au7-lai5 Am3-lun5 hou7 Ap-sa-liong5 thai5 si2). Lu2-seng3 ah! Lin2 tioh8 keng2-seng2, tioh8 chhiat-chhiat ki3-sim, lin2 si7 choe3 seng5-siu7 e5 hong-bin7, lang5 thau-chiah8 khi3 lah, choe7 e5 cheng2-chi2 si7 tiam3 ti7 li2 e5 chhan5, giat8-thai am3-kiat, hit si5 beh an2-choaN2 liau2-khiok. 
