  Na7-si7 Lan5-hiong iau-ki koh sit-tng3, phun-pho chhoe7 ai3-cheng5 e5 siu5-jin5, thiau3-chui2 chu7-sat, chhi3 keng2-chhat-kiok8 liu5-ti3 e5 chu-bi7, siu7 keng2-chhat e5 hou7-sang3, siu7 lang5 phui3-noa7 bih-chhui3; kau3 chia lai5 Lan5-hiong chin-chiaN3 si7 sim, sin long2 ia3-sian7, seng-khu koh u7 sin, na2 tu2 in lau7-pe7 3 e7 tin5-tiau5 e7 tiau5, chu7-te2 kui7-leh teh hau2, siau7 3 e7 chu7 an2-ni un loh8-khi3 to2 tui3 thou5-kha loh8-khi3. In a-che2 Lan5-eng koaN2-kin2 oa2--lai5, tui3 a-pa e5 chhiu2 ka7 i liah8-leh; in a-pa khi3 chit8 e7 chu7 an2-ni the tui3 piah-nih loh8 khi3, the tiam3 hia chhoan2; toa7-che2 Lan5-eng tit8-tit8 kio3 a-pa m7-kaN2, the3 in sio2-moai7 kui7 in a-pa. Sio2-moai7 Lan5-ji5 khoaN3 a-che2 un-to2 tui3 thou5-kha loh8 khi3, kin2 khi3 hu5 in a-che2, hau2 a-che2, ji5-au7 Lan5-ji5 ia7 khui-siaN hau2 “A-pa5-ah m7-kaN2 a3 lah.” Lan5-hiohg ka-ki7 ia7 hau2 m7-kaN2, peh khi2--lai5 eng7 pe5--e5 pe5 kau3 in a-pa e5 bin7-cheng5 koh tit8-tit8 kio3 m7-kaN2, kau3 chia i chiah chhim-chhim thong3-kam2 i e5 choe7 e5 thang kiaN, chit8 lai7-bin7 chhiong-moa2 thi5-khau3 e5 siaN, 3 e5 kiaN2 long2 kui7-kui7 ti7 bin7-cheng5. 
